{"tid":2318518,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"擲物堵鐵路案 辯方質疑沒記錄被告對話內容 警：佢冇答我咪冇寫低","createTime":"2020-12-09T11:26:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-09T11:32:43.000Z","uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7a721de69a42bed8da6c2a5c0ce99f632b45f1f4","tid":2318518,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T11:26:42.000Z","msg":"網民去年11月發起「黎明行動」，圖堵塞交通兼發起三罷，東鐵線大埔段路軌被人投擲竹枝，事後有7人被控有意圖地將物品放在或擲於鐵路上等罪，其中四人否認控罪，案件今於粉嶺裁判法院續審。其中有份追截案中被告地盤工的警員指，被告被捕後沒有回應提問。辯方質疑警員未有將對話記錄下來，警員謂：「佢冇答，所以我咪冇寫低。」<br />\n<br />\n惟辯方發現有關對話從未於口供內記錄下來，警員同意，但指「佢冇答，所以我咪冇寫低」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n主控傳召最後一名證人後稱「控方案情暫時完結」，語畢隨即被裁判官黃國輝大聲喝斥：「你解釋下咩叫暫時吖，你唔係layman嚟㗎，你專業啲啦，主控。唔通一陣你又話未完咁呀？」主控於是以英文謂「close my case」，黃官即稱：「哦，原來識英文，但中文唔好。」場面尷尬。"},{"pid":"c7b6550fd6ea0e5ab744beced62ed19a377f913d","tid":2318518,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T11:26:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201209/4G5MU4VC35FEPBNB453IQZG37I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201209%2F4G5MU4VC35FEPBNB453IQZG37I%2F&d=zhjqHwqbwmwTWRz%2FWGYaUEZHjOsADYkIOf4eYSwfwZo%3D&h=e47d9438\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201209%2F4G5MU4VC35FEPBNB453IQZG37I%2F&h=3fa4020d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201209/4G5MU4VC35FEPBNB453IQZG37I/</a>"},{"pid":"fe943464a826dfca7b0afe7ad038b104162de1fa","tid":2318518,"uid":283700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T11:29:26.000Z","msg":"主控：諗到再問 剎那間問佢博佢答係<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8fbb2fbc24a859f419fa9f854ef539f33adcddb","tid":2318518,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T11:32:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face